- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper presents a new consensus algorithm, which is a fundamental problem in distributed computing and falls under this sub-category. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the performance of the proposed algorithm in geo-distributed experiments, which involves control and optimization of systems.
